vote.title: Authorize Supplemental Agreement No. 2 to the Multiple Use Agreement with the Texas Department of Transportation to include additional right-of-way adjacent to Interstate Highway (IH) 345 and Carpenter Park and adjacent to IH 45 and Martin Luther King Jr. Boulevard and remove right-of-way adjacent to IH 345 and Canton Street from the original agreement - Financing: No cost consideration to the City (This item was deferred on May 27, 2020)
